00:04:28.880 --> 00:04:32.900
This right here, this right here is called
the trunk.

00:04:32.900 --> 00:04:37.350
And the, the skin of the trunk is called the
bark.

00:04:37.350 --> 00:04:45.640
Up there you have a branch, and if we look
