00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:53.040
So there's also the parts of the tree that
we refer to after it has been cut down or

00:04:53.040 --> 00:04:54.980
after it has died.

00:04:54.980 --> 00:04:56.810
This is a stick.

00:04:56.810 --> 00:04:58.420
