00:04:58.420 --> 00:05:02.600
Logs are generally used to make lumber to
build houses.

00:05:02.600 --> 00:05:07.510
And sticks are used for, well, just about
everything including roasting marshmallows

00:05:07.510 --> 00:05:09.700
